{
  "stem": "2996.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not far from where we lived, there was a little park-- the Teutoburg Park.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Teutoburg was in the year nine, the Germans defeated the Romans in the Teutoburg Wald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wald is world, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was our neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in many of these neighborhoods, you had fussball clubs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a Jewish fussball club.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we have to go and play against other teams.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we always won.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know what drove us?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because people didn't like us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many a time, after the game was over, there was-- were fights, like you still have in Germany, not only by the children, by the old one.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If the Italians and the Germans fight, many a time, they [INAUDIBLE], but not only the players themselves, the public too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had fights many a time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd call us the Schweinhunds, Judeschweinhunds-- you know, things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that too had an impact on my life later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Um hm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the one thing that again had an impact on me later on was-- what do they call these people who blew up the big building in Oklahoma City-- they call them--",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the militia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have something similar to the militia there against the government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the government was run by the traitors who signed the Versailles Treaty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first thing they were going to do is eliminate that government and gain back what was called the Polish Corridor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Should I explain what the Polish Corridor is, or can I assume that they do know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's one thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other thing is they were-- that this was the first time since the end of World War I that a Jew was a member of the cabinet-- Walter Rathenau-- Walter, W-A-L-T-E-R.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
